Service of Mediatek HotKnot features, icluding message transmission, file transmission through the HotKnot technology.

This library is pre-built by MediaTek internal.


WHAT IT DOES?
=============
HotKnotConnectivity.apk contains MediaTek developed HotKnot connectivity service
It can help to transfer file through Bluetooth OPP.
Without them, HotKnot functionalities with Bluetooth will not work

HOW IT WAS BUILT?
==================
1. The featureoption MTK_HOTKNOT_SUPPORT should be true.



[Build Method]

make HotKnotConnectivity
or
mmm vendor/mediatek/proprietary/packages/apps/HotKnotConnectivity



HOW TO USE IT?
==============

1) enter Settings page and press HotKnot On/Off

2) if enable it , will show the HotKnot icon on the status bar to tell user HotKnot is on
All the source code of this module were written by MediaTek co..
